ZH: 1. 万事大吉，今天是个幸运的日子。
EN: Everything will go well, today is a lucky day.
ZH: 2. 无论发生什么事情，最终一切都会万事大吉。
EN: No matter what happens, in the end, everything will turn out fine.
ZH: 3. 我祝你新年快乐，万事大吉。
EN: I wish you a happy New Year, and may everything go well.
ZH: 4. 在这个重要的时刻，我只想说一句话：万事大吉！
EN: At this crucial moment, I just want to say one thing: Best of luck!
ZH: 5. 无论你去哪里，我都祝你万事大吉。
EN: Wherever you go, I wish you good luck.
ZH: 6. 做好准备，因为明天将会万事大吉。
EN: Be prepared, for tomorrow will bring good fortune.
ZH: 7. 万事大吉是我对你最真挚的祝福。
EN: Best of luck is my sincerest wish for you.
ZH: 8. 不要担心，只要你尽力就一定会万事大吉。
EN: Don't worry, as long as you do your best, everything will turn out fine.
ZH: 9. 困境中，我相信你能够度过并且万事大吉。
EN: In times of hardship, I believe you can overcome it and all will be well.
ZH: 10. 当你有困难时，只需要相信自己，就能够迎接万事大吉的未来。
EN: When you face difficulties, just believe in yourself, and a future full of good luck awaits.
ZH: 11. 万事大吉只等你抓住机会。
EN: Good luck is waiting for you, just seize the opportunity.
ZH: 12. 张开双臂，迎接幸运和万事大吉。
EN: Open your arms and embrace luck and good fortune.
ZH: 13. 坚持下去，一定会有万事大吉的一天。
EN: Keep going, there will surely be a day of good fortune.
ZH: 14. 万事大吉是你努力后的回报。
EN: Good luck is the reward for your hard work.
ZH: 15. 祝你新的开始，万事大吉。
EN: Wishing you a new beginning and good fortune.
ZH: 16. 在这个挑战充满的旅程中，愿你的每一天都万事大吉。
EN: In this challenging journey, may every day bring you good fortune.
ZH: 17. 不论遇到什么困难，你都能够坚持下去并且万事大吉。
EN: No matter what difficulties you encounter, I believe you can persevere and have good luck.
ZH: 18. 无论前方有多少障碍，只要你相信，一切都会万事大吉。
EN: No matter how many obstacles lay ahead, as long as you believe, everything will turn out fine.
ZH: 19. 学业有成，万事大吉。
EN: May you excel in your studies, and everything goes well.
ZH: 20. 无论遇到什么困难，一定要相信自己，然后万事大吉。
EN: No matter what difficulties you face, always believe in yourself, and then everything will be fine.
